channel.title: Project X Scape [INFORMATION]
channel.description:
[b][center][size=20pt][font=Arial]Hi There![/font][/size][/center]
[center][b]As you may of noticed I am starting to code again ;), I thought I might give all you Mopar Users a sneak peak of what i have to offer.
Heres a list of what i have so far:
[ul][li]All NPC's in Varrock & Lumby - taken from RS[/li] [li]All Shops in Varrock & Lumby - taken from RS[/li] [li]Defenders - taken from RS[/li] [li]New Graphics and Interfaces - taken from RS[/li] [li]Full working Prayer! - thanks Zerofreeze fixed all :)[/li] [li]Seers village with Hidden Rock Crabs - taken from RS[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]I changed the way you get runes, from altars and abyss, no ::runes[/li] [li]Make you all train slower, harder to get levels[/li] [li]GUI Package, with Miss Silab. and AntiCheat + my own SkillEditor GUI [/li][/ul] [/center]
[center] [b]No Pictures for anyones knowledge!
If you would like to find out more PM Me!
WARNING! No SPAM and this is only an Information! [DEVELOPMENT][/b][/center]
